51

00:02:53,920  -->  00:02:55,480
By the end of this lesson,

52

00:02:55,480  -->  00:02:59,380
you will define and invoke your own user defined functions,

53

00:02:59,380  -->  00:03:02,060
understand how arguments and parameters work,

54

00:03:02,060  -->  00:03:05,640
and learn how Python handles exceptions and errors.

55

00:03:05,640  -->  00:03:09,740
If you're ready to take your Python skills to the next level,

56

00:03:09,740  -->  00:03:14,400
let's dive into the world of functions and exceptions.
